title: rivr
abstract: >-
  An agent-focused, read-only CLI for Amazon Shopping search and data retrieval, with a
  pluggable backend (SerpApi, Rainforest, official Amazon Creators API, or keyless
  scraping), built to the Agent CLI Guidelines.
type: software
authors:
